- title "Clients"
%p.tile Whether it was graphics or a full production, we have done work for these people on some capacity over the last few years. Rollover below for some testimonials.

.clients

  - @clients.each_with_index do |client, index|

    .client.tile
      .overlay
      = image_tag client.logo_url
    .client-description
      %h3.client-name= client.name
      %p.client-description= client.description
    - if index % 6 == 5
      .details
        .client-info.description.tile
